examples.translation: 私の曾祖母はFronniahという名前でした。

etymology.value: Origin uncertain, possibly a variant of another name or a newly coined name.

usage_notes.explanation: The name Fronniah is very uncommon and may be unfamiliar to many people.

readability_explanation.text: The name Fronniah is very rare, so it is unlikely to be encountered frequently. It is primarily of interest to those studying names or genealogy.
